b.com/bfs/storyff/_00000h74lwtegpvqe2giv251nzonkbb_firsti.jpg", "pub_location": "江苏", "cover43": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/43d69d3284d1cc71d4f5a2b29d452b46708404bd.jpg", "tidv2": 2188, "tnamev2": "自我成长", "pid_v2": 1027, "pid_name_v2": "情感", "bvid": "BV1gVN16fEs5", "season_type": 0, "is_ogv": false, "ogv_info": null, "enable_vt": 0, "ai_rcmd": null, "rcmd_reason": {"content": "百万播放", "corner_mark": 1}}, {"aid": 116924545634684, "videos": 1, "tid": 201, "tname": "科学科普", "copyright": 3, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/15e0b45c7599efa66898df5392baf7ec0c7d5fee.jpg", "title": "42度高温来了：今年最热时段还未到来，暴雨又赖上广西等地了", "pubdate": 1784127224, "ctime": 1784127224, "desc": "这两天，我国迎来大范围酷热高温，其中川渝一带成了我国最热的地方之一。7月14-15日，重庆北碚等地连续两天42度，市区沙坪坝连续两天41度，全市河谷地区几乎全部都在40度以上。与此同时，新疆吐鲁番，内蒙古西北部沙漠地区，北京天津河北中部，以及长江中下游都非常热，7月15日早晨8点前后，江苏无锡在早高峰中超过35度。下午宁波鄞州达到38.9度，上海徐家汇也达到38.9度，与此同时相对湿度仍然很高，体感温度达到48度上下，上海市区也成为整个东部最热的地方。长三角很多地方在凌晨0点前后，体感温度甚至都还有40度", "state": 0, "duration": 211, "mission_id": 4065027, "rights": {"bp": 0, "elec": 0, "download": 0, "movie": 0, "pay": 0, "hd5": 0, "no_reprint": 0, "autoplay": 1, "ugc_pay": 0, "is_cooperation": 0, "ugc_pay_preview": 0, "no_background": 0, "arc_pay": 0, "pay_free_watch": 0}, "owner": {"mid": 547072854, "name": "中气爱", "face": "https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/face/e5f6be30a18988ed92f677e6a47a346270172081.jpg"}, "stat": {"aid": 116924545634684, "view": 354925, "danmaku": 861, "reply": 2948, "favorite": 1323, "coin": 639, "share": 1492, "now_rank": 0, "his_rank": 0, "like": 19752, "dislike": 0, "vt": 0, "vv": 354925, "fav_g": 0, "like_g": 0}, "dynamic": "", "cid": 39983383951, "dimension": {"width": 1920, "height": 1080, "rotate": 0}, "short_link_v2": "https://b23.tv/BV19FNz65EjT", "first_frame": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/storyff/_00002ryn5i1o72r4n2kf3t6yedb7gcb_firsti.jpg", "pub_location": "江苏", "cover43": "http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a3c07c0445bb79818293608e1cf9126d8a9cad7c.jpg", "tidv2": 2207, "tnamev2": "随拍·综合", "pid_v2": 1032, "pid_name_v2": "其他", "bvi